research/history/logs/agent_action_0150.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，{b_i^sh} 是 shared 静态库，{b_{e,j}} 是 routed expert 静态子库，{c_m} 是全局 residual 静态补偿库，x_stage1 是 shared+routed factorized stage 的重构。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“shared library lookup + routed expert sublibrary lookup + residual lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：在保持 r146 的 matched recipe（K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224、STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 与其余训练配方不变）的前提下，新加 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 能回答当前最缺的结构问题：把 hetero MoE 的 shared+routed factorized head 再接上 residual cleanup，是否能在约 0.47x total_cost 下形成比现有 `<0.5x` anchor 更有价值的新结构段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["若该点在约 0.47x 下优于当前 `<0.5x` 最佳 FVU=0.1010，则下一轮只改 `K` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，把这条新 hetero-MoE+residual 线继续向左压缩。","若该点接近但未优于 r146，则说明 factorized shared+routed stage 确有结构价值但不足以取代 trunk；后续可只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 验证瓶颈是否在 shared basis 宽度。","若该点明显劣于 r146 且不优于 r147/r148，则可更明确地终止当前 target 上“shared+routed factorized + residual”这条方向，避免继续在 hetero factorized family 上耗费预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual`，真实修改文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","本地 allowlist 校验通过：`validate_env_overrides` 现在接受 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 搭配 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`NUM_EXPERTS`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`STAGE1_RATIO`。","按架构接线 checklist 做了 exact smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual, K=112, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=1499136、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=1957888，对 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.47，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也左于 r146 matched recipe 的约 0.54x。","最近三条 fresh 结构对照结果分别是 r147 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` FVU=0.1038、r148 `two_stage_residual_expert` FVU=0.1140、r149 `factorized_expert_topk` FVU=0.2450；因此继续在这些已有 family 上做局部扫参的信息增量很低，本轮更适合补最小新原型。"],"reference_round":146,"self_review":"这轮选择 `edit_sae_code` 而不是再做现有 family 的 param-only probe，原因是当前已连续三轮 fresh 结构对照都未形成新非支配点，而提示明确要求在这种情况下优先切换到新的结构假设或新增最小可运行原型。新 family 不是无约束扩张：它直接填补了当前最缺的“shared experts + routed experts + expert-internal low-rank + residual cleanup”槽位，并且只复用现有 tunable 参数，没有新增 env key。风险在于 residual_encoder 仍然较重，可能重复 r147 的结论；但这次 factorized stage 把 stage1 selection 从约 0.44x 压到约 0.36x，足以提供新的结构信息。","summary":"已新增并接线 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual`，建议以 r146 为 reference，仅设置 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 启动首轮真实训练。它是一个已落盘、已 smoke、已过 allowlist 的最小新 family，目标是在当前最需要补证据的 0.3x-0.5x 带直接回答“hetero MoE 的 factorized shared+routed stage 加 residual cleanup”是否值得继续。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0138.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{l∈S_res(r1(x))} γ_l(x) c_l，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，r1(x)=x-Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i-Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}；U={u_i} 是静态 shared low-rank library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库，C={c_l} 是静态 residual library。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + 少量 routed experts 选择 + 静态库查表加权和 + 选择性 residual 补偿”，不依赖动态生成字典，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：当前最有信息量但尚无最小原型的槽位，不是再扫现有 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 hidden/K 邻域，而是给这条 hetero MoE 线补上一段全局 residual cleanup。相对 r134 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual cleanup”能否在约 0.60x total_cost 的中低成本带形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该新 family 在约 0.60x 下明显优于 r134 且接近当前中成本最优点，则下一轮优先修好该 architecture 的 override allowlist，然后只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，区分瓶颈是在 stage1 shared+routed 容量还是 residual cleanup 配额。","如果该点有正信号但成本偏重，则下一轮在接好 allowlist 后只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 之一，测试 hetero MoE + residual 能否继续左移。","如果该点明显弱于 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 或只小幅优于 r134，则可较清晰判定 residual 增益不足以抵消 shared+routed 的额外复杂度，后续应把预算转回别的兼容结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","本地编译通过：`python -m py_compile sparsify/config.py sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual, K=128, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，按 r134 配方（`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`）本地估算 selection≈0.47x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.60x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","本轮实际运行时相对 r134 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`；没有新增 env key，也没有改执行层语义。"],"reference_round":134,"self_review":"满足运行时单变量原则：计划运行时相对 r134 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 的旧 family 局部扫参，而是补齐当前高优先级但尚未实现的“hetero MoE + residual cleanup”最小原型。代码改动严格限制在 `sparsify/`，并已按 `sae-architecture-integration` 完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class 和 exact architecture smoke。主要风险是 residual encoder 的 1024x1024 选择成本本身就接近 0.25x，可能让该 family 的总成本落在 0.60x 左右却仍拿不到足够 FVU 改善；但这正是当前最需要的新结构证据。","summary":"已在 `sparsify/` 落盘最小新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`：把当前最有希望的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 接上一段全局 sparse residual cleanup。建议本轮以 r134 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，先做一次干净的 matched architecture swap，直接判断“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual”是否值得继续。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0038.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":37,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_total_cost","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差做 sparse cleanup，因此仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。r37 已经证明该 family 在 K=192、EF=1 下可给出很强质量信号；本轮相对 r37 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK: 384 -> 128`，主假设是当前 trunk 明显过重，降低 trunk rank 后仍能保留大部分重构质量，同时把 total_cost 从约 1.06x 压到约 0.69x，直接补当前更需要的低到中成本 Pareto 段。","summary":"沿着已验证有效的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 主线做单变量降成本回退，而不是切回旧 family。以 r37 为参考只降 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 128，测试该三段式结构能否以明显更低 total_cost 保持接近 r37 的低 FVU。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r37 只修改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这是当前信息增量最高的动作，因为 r37 已给出强质量锚点，下一步最应该回答的是这条新 Pareto 段能否往低成本方向延伸，而不是继续在同一高成本点附近微调 `STAGE1_RATIO`。`TRUNK_RANK=128` 还能同时降低 encoder 与 deployment 成本，归因清晰。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 仍维持明显优于现有 <0.8x 区域 anchor 的 FVU，则下一轮继续保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=192` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，细化这条新 Pareto 段的形状。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 FVU 退化过大，则说明该 family 质量主要依赖较重 trunk；下一轮优先回到 `TRUNK_RANK=192` 做中间点，而不是继续压得更低。","如果该 family 在降成本后仍然保持竞争力，则 `two-stage residual expert` 的优先级可以暂时后移，因为当前 family 已经回答了三段式结构值得继续。"],"notes_to_memory":["r37 `lowrank_expert_residual K=192 EF=1` 已给出强质量锚点，memory 中记录的 FVU 约为 0.0424。","`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","按当前实现的成本估算，`TRUNK_RANK=128` 时 combined_ratio 约 0.69x，显著低于 r37 的约 1.06x，同时仍在硬约束内。","Round 38 应优先回答这条新 family 是否能向低中成本带延展，而不是回到 plain selector 家族继续扫 K。"],"touched_files":[]}
