research/history/logs/agent_action_0142.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(h(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，{b_i^sh} 是 shared 静态向量库，{b_{e,j}} 是 routed expert 静态子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r123 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared+routed 异构 MoE 中把 expert 内部 scorer 也做低秩化”是否能在约 0.22x total_cost 下形成新的低成本结构段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.22x 下明显优于现有 0.22x-0.25x frontier，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，继续压缩 hetero MoE 的低秩路由链路。","如果该点仍明显落后于当前 low-cost frontier，则可以更有把握地下调“fully factorized hetero MoE”优先级，把后续预算转向其他结构槽位，而不是继续在 shared+routed 低秩变体上反复试错。","如果结果只小幅优于 `expert_topk` 但仍被 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 支配，则说明 shared branch 有价值，但 routed experts 过度低秩化会伤害质量；后续应优先保留 expert-specific full heads 或切向别的 staged/residual 结构。"],"notes_to_memory":["r141 已说明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 在约 0.30x total_cost 下仍被当前 low-cost frontier 压制，因此“shared low-rank basis + full expert head”这条无 residual 线可暂时降级。","本轮改做另一条 hetero MoE 结构对照：相对 r123 只切 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，用同一低成本 anchor 直接测试 expert 内部低秩 scorer 是否值得继续。","本地成本自检：在 r123 配方下切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 后，selection_accesses=450560、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=909312，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.22，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":123,"self_review":"这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮非支配失败、`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 也已给出新的负信号后，继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩信息增量偏低；切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前对异构 MoE 与 expert-internal low-rank 的优先级，也能在更低的 0.22x 成本带补一段此前仍欠清晰的结构证据。主要风险是该 family 在旧轮次已有弱负信号，但当前这次是与 r123 严格 matched-cost 的 fresh validation，结论更有解释力。","summary":"建议以 r123 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`。这是一轮低成本异构 MoE 结构重验：直接测试“shared+routed + expert 内部低秩 scorer”能否在约 0.22x total_cost 下提供比当前 low-cost frontier 更有价值的新段。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0155.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + 轻量 router 选少量 experts + shared lookup + expert-local top-k lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答当前最高优先级的 hetero-MoE 结构“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local head / local top-k”在约 0.28x total_cost 下，是否能优于现有 0.28x-0.32x 低成本 frontier 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下接近或优于当前 0.28x-0.32x anchors，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，测试 shared scorer 还能否继续左移而不明显掉质。","如果该点仍明显落后于同成本 frontier，则不要继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上做局部扫参，下一轮切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 做同 recipe 的 matched architecture probe。","如果结果异常差且与历史 r141 同向，可把“shared low-rank basis + routed local head”在当前 target 的低成本主线优先级下调，转回别的未充分验证结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["当前代码已支持 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，本轮不需要新增 tunable，也不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。","已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=96, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 可正常运行。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=794624，deployment_accesses=393216，combined_accesses=1187840，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.28，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮是对当前 operator hint 明确优先的 hetero-MoE 方向做 matched-cost 重验，不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 上做旧 family 局部微调。"],"reference_round":152,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。我没有返回代码改动，因为当前高优先级候选 family 已经落盘且可运行；本轮更需要的是用当前低成本 anchor recipe 做一次干净的 matched architecture swap。选择这条线而不是继续调 `lowrank_expert_*`，是因为运行时提示已明确把“shared experts + routed experts，尤其 shared low-rank basis + expert-local top-k”列为当前最值得补的结构证据。主要风险是该 family 在旧轮次已有弱负信号；但那些结果主要来自更早的 112/128 recipe，本轮用当前 `K=96, latents_per_expert=224` 的低成本配方重验，归因更直接。","summary":"建议本轮以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。这是一次面向 0.28x 低成本带的 matched hetero-MoE 结构探针，直接验证当前最高优先级方向“shared low-rank basis + routed expert local top-k”是否能形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0156.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert-local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r155 已经把 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 明确证伪为当前 0.28x 低成本带的有效前沿候选，因此下一步不应继续在同一 family 上做局部扫参，而应切到另一条仍符合当前 agenda 的新结构槽位。相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”在约 0.28x total_cost 下是否比已失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更接近当前低成本 frontier。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下明显优于 r155 且接近当前 0.28x-0.30x frontier，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，定位 coarse stage 与 residual expert 的分工边界。","如果该点仍明显落后于同成本 frontier，则可把 shared-lowrank 两段式方向在当前 target 的低成本主线优先级下调，下一轮转向更中成本但更有希望形成新段的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` matched probe。","如果该点仅小幅优于 r155 但仍不进入非支配前沿，则记录为 shared-lowrank coarse 比 shared-lowrank routed 更稳，但仍不足以替代现有 low-cost anchors，后续不要继续在该 family 上做连续局部微调。"],"notes_to_memory":["r155 已落盘：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 实际 FVU=0.14630839228630066，显著落后当前 0.28x-0.30x 低成本 frontier，因此不应继续在该 family 上做局部扫参。","当前代码已支持 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，本轮不需要新增 tunable，也不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。","已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert, K=96, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可正常运行。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=794624，deployment_accesses=393216，combined_accesses=1187840，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.28，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮是对另一条高优先级结构槽位 `two-stage residual expert` 的 matched-cost 重验，不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或已失败的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。"],"reference_round":152,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以不继续沿 r155 的 family 压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，是因为该 family 已在 128/112/96 三个成本配方上持续给出一致负信号；当前更高信息量的动作是切到尚未在现行 `K=96` 低成本 recipe 下复验的 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。本轮没有返回代码改动，因为该 family 已经落盘且本地 smoke 通过；主要风险是它在 r144 的 K=112 recipe 下也表现偏弱，但正因为 r155 已证明 routed top-k 线不足，当前最需要回答的是两段式 residual cleanup 是否比 routed-topk 更适合这个低成本带。","summary":"建议本轮以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。这是一次面向 0.28x 低成本带的 matched architecture probe，用来回答 shared-lowrank 两段式 residual expert 是否比刚失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0141.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r123 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，直接做一次 matched-cost hetero-MoE 结构对照，回答“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local head”这条线在约 0.30x total_cost 下是否能形成比当前 low-cost anchor 更有价值的新结构段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.30x 下明显优于现有 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 邻近锚点，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 继续压低 shared/routed 成本。","如果该点仍被当前 0.28x-0.30x frontier 支配，则可更明确地下调“无 residual 的 shared-lowrank+routed”优先级，把后续预算转回别的结构槽位，而不是继续在这条 family 上做局部扫参。","如果结果介于 r123 与当前 0.30x anchor 之间，则说明 shared low-rank basis 有一定价值但单独不足以形成新段；后续应优先考虑带 residual 的版本或新的 staged expert 结构，而不是再压同一 recipe。"],"notes_to_memory":["r139-r140 已说明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮未形成新非支配点；本轮按策略切回新的结构假设对照，而不是继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩。","本轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做旧 family 局部微调，而是以当前低成本 reference r123 为 matched baseline，直接重验更符合当前 agenda 的 hetero MoE 结构 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。","本地成本自检：在 r123 配方下切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 后，selection_accesses=794624、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=1253376，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.30，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":123,"self_review":"这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 已连续两轮未形成新非支配点后，继续沿同一 family 做 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `K` 的局部扫参信息增量偏低；切回 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做 matched-cost architecture swap，更符合当前“结构扩展优先”和对 hetero MoE 的明确优先级。主要风险是该 family 先前在更高容量配方下已有负信号；但当前这次是更低成本、与 low-cost anchor 严格对照的重验，结论会更清晰。","summary":"建议以 r123 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。这是一轮面向低成本前沿的 matched-cost 结构对照，用当前最相关的 low-cost anchor 直接回答“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”是否值得继续，而不是继续在最近连续失利的 residual 变体上做局部压缩。","touched_files":[]}
