research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:64:    "description": "已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`：shared 分支保留低秩 scorer，routed experts 改回 full-dim local heads，用来做对 r127-r128 的最小结构修正。建议本轮以 r128 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，用同配方直接判断当前 shared+routed 负信号是否主要来自过度 factorize routed experts。",
